.TH verse-dialog 1 "Bible Verse" "DEBIAN" \" -*- nroff -*-
.SH NAME
verse-dialog \- Displays a daily devotional verse from scripture
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBverse-dialog\fP
.SH DESCRIPTION
Displays a verse taken from the database in
.B /usr/share/verse/daily.verse
that is specific for the current date.  verse-dialog uses dialog to 
display the verse in a pseudo-window, thus allowing verse to be used
from a menu running under X.
.SH AUTHOR
